Head. Area between frontal crests reaching or slightly exceeding the level of crests in dorsal view; malar space less than or equal to distance between antennal sockets; 
length
of postocellar area about 2 times of lateral ocellus diameter; maximal length of temple 1.25-1.45 times greater than its minimal length; flagellum 2.3-2.6 times longer than breadth of head.
